{File:UUP_IS.txt  Index:18  Index Date:20181029  PL:78.57%  PS:21.43%  Trades:14  CL:1}

IF CLOSE OF 7 BARS AGO > CLOSE OF 5 BARS AGO
AND CLOSE OF 5 BARS AGO > CLOSE OF 6 DAYS AGO
AND CLOSE OF 6 BARS AGO > CLOSE OF 10 BARS AGO
AND CLOSE OF 10 BARS AGO > CLOSE OF 9 BARS AGO
THEN BUY NEXT BAR ON THE OPEN WITH
PROFIT TARGET AT ENTRY PRICE + 0.598562 %
AND STOP LOSS AT ENTRY PRICE - 0.663625 %
